cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV 

This paper involves the use of a quadcopter for navigation and control, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques such as supervised and reinforcement learning, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The task of mapping natural language instructions to physical quadcopter control involves natural language processing (NLP), which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves the use of simulation for training the model, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV).
